Title: Schwinger terms in gravitation in two dimensions as a consequence of the

gravitational anomalyAuthors: Emmanuel Kohlprath

Comments: 8 pages, Latex, additional references

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 43 (2002) 4898-4903

We compute the Schwinger term in the gravitational constraints in twodimensions, starting from the path integral in Hamiltonian form and theEinstein anomaly.